            <div><span class="t-err">  ✗</span>  <span class="t-str">assets/vendor-CHmL3xRz.js</span><span class="t-dim">: 18.7 kB exceeds 15 kB </span><span class="t-warn">(+25%)</span></div>
            <div><span class="t-err">  error</span>  <span class="t-dim">1 budget violation. Build failed.</span></div>
