        <div class="features">
          <div class="feat"><span class="feat-icon">📊</span><div class="feat-title">Asset table</div><p class="feat-desc">Every JS and CSS file with its size printed after every build.</p></div>
          <div class="feat"><span class="feat-icon">📄</span><div class="feat-title">Per-page breakdown</div><p class="feat-desc">See exactly how much JS/CSS each page pulls in across all assets.</p></div>
          <div class="feat"><span class="feat-icon">🗜️</span><div class="feat-title">Compression-aware</div><p class="feat-desc">Set budgets against gzip or brotli — the wire size that actually matters.</p></div>
          <div class="feat"><span class="feat-icon">🚦</span><div class="feat-title">Fails CI</div><p class="feat-desc">Exits with code 1 on violation. Works with any CI pipeline, no config.</p></div>
          <div class="feat"><span class="feat-icon">🎯</span><div class="feat-title">Glob rules</div><p class="feat-desc">Target vendor chunks, specific files, or all JS/CSS with minimatch globs.</p></div>
          <div class="feat"><span class="feat-icon">📋</span><div class="feat-title">JSON report</div><p class="feat-desc">Write a machine-readable report to diff bundle growth between deploys.</p></div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Env Inspector preview -->
      <section class="section">
        <p class="section-eyebrow">astro-env-inspector</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">Your env vars,<br />always in reach.</h2>
        <p class="section-desc">Click the key icon in the dev toolbar. Every variable from your <code style="font-family:var(--ffm);font-size:14px;background:var(--bg-pill);padding:2px 7px;border-radius:4px">.env</code> files appears — grouped, masked, and searchable.</p>

        <div class="terminal">
          <div class="terminal-bar">
            <span class="t-dot red"></span><span class="t-dot yellow"></span><span class="t-dot green"></span>
            <span class="terminal-title">Env Inspector — dev toolbar</span>
          </div>
          <div class="terminal-body">
            <div><span class="t-dim">  🌐  PUBLIC (PUBLIC_*)</span></div>
            <div>  <span class="t-ok">●</span>  <span class="t-key">PUBLIC_SITE_NAME       </span>  <span class="t-str">My Astro Site</span></div>
            <div>  <span class="t-ok">●</span>  <span class="t-key">PUBLIC_API_URL         </span>  <span class="t-str">https://api.example.com</span></div>
            <div>  <span class="t-warn">●</span>  <span class="t-warn">PUBLIC_API_KEY         </span>  <span class="t-dim">••••••••</span>  <span class="t-warn">⚠ leaking</span></div>
            <br />
            <div><span class="t-dim">  🔒  PRIVATE / SERVER-ONLY</span></div>
            <div>  <span class="t-ok">●</span>  <span class="t-key">DATABASE_URL           </span>  <span class="t-str">postgres://localhost/db</span></div>
            <div>  <span class="t-ok">●</span>  <span class="t-key">STRIPE_SECRET_KEY      </span>  <span class="t-dim">••••••••</span>  <span class="t-dim">👁</span></div>
            <div>  <span class="t-err">●</span>  <span class="t-dim">SENDGRID_API_KEY       </span>  <span class="t-dim">not set</span></div>
            <br />
            <div><span class="t-dim">  🚀  ASTRO BUILT-INS</span></div>
            <div>  <span class="t-ok">●</span>  <span class="t-key">MODE                   </span>  <span class="t-str">development</span></div>
            <div>  <span class="t-ok">●</span>  <span class="t-key">DEV                    </span>  <span class="t-str">true</span></div>
            <div>  <span class="t-ok">●</span>  <span class="t-key">BASE_URL               </span>  <span class="t-str">/</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="features">
          <div class="feat"><span class="feat-icon">🔒</span><div class="feat-title">Dev-only</div><p class="feat-desc">Completely stripped in <code>astro build</code>. Zero production footprint, guaranteed.</p></div>
          <div class="feat"><span class="feat-icon">📋</span><div class="feat-title">Grouped</div><p class="feat-desc">Public, private, Astro built-ins — each in their own section for quick scanning.</p></div>
          <div class="feat"><span class="feat-icon">⚠️</span><div class="feat-title">Leak detection</div><p class="feat-desc">Warns when a <code>PUBLIC_*</code> var looks like it contains a secret key or token.</p></div>
          <div class="feat"><span class="feat-icon">👁</span><div class="feat-title">Masked by default</div><p class="feat-desc">Sensitive values hidden with a per-variable reveal toggle — safe for screen shares.</p></div>
          <div class="feat"><span class="feat-icon">🔍</span><div class="feat-title">Searchable</div><p class="feat-desc">Filter by key or value in real time across all variables.</p></div>
          <div class="feat"><span class="feat-icon">📋</span><div class="feat-title">Copy on click</div><p class="feat-desc">Copy any value to clipboard instantly without leaving the browser.</p></div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Route Map preview -->
      <section class="section">
        <p class="section-eyebrow">astro-toolbar-routes</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">Every route,<br />one click away.</h2>
        <p class="section-desc">Click the map icon in the dev toolbar and every route in your project appears — grouped, searchable, and navigable. No more typing URLs by hand.</p>

        <div class="terminal">
          <div class="terminal-bar">
            <span class="t-dot red"></span><span class="t-dot yellow"></span><span class="t-dot green"></span>
            <span class="terminal-title">Route Map — dev toolbar</span>
          </div>
          <div class="terminal-body">
            <div><span class="t-ok">●</span> <span class="t-str">7 static</span>  <span class="t-err">●</span> <span class="t-dim">1 SSR</span>  <span class="t-dim">●</span> <span class="t-dim">1 endpoint</span></div>
            <br />
            <div><span class="t-dim">  📄  PAGES</span></div>
