            <div>  <span class="t-ok">●</span>  <span class="t-warn">/blog/[slug]               </span>  <span class="t-warn">dynamic</span>  <span class="t-err">SSR</span></div>
            <div>  <span class="t-ok">●</span>  <span class="t-str">/contact                   </span>  <span class="t-dim">→</span></div>
            <div>  <span class="t-ok">●</span>  <span class="t-str">/pricing                   </span>  <span class="t-dim">→</span></div>
            <div>  <span class="t-ok">●</span>  <span class="t-str">/rss.xml                   </span>  <span class="t-dim">→</span></div>
            <br />
            <div><span class="t-dim">  ⚡  ENDPOINTS</span></div>
            <div>  <span class="t-ok">●</span>  <span class="t-str">/api/contact               </span>  <span class="t-info">endpoint</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="features">
          <div class="feat"><span class="feat-icon">🖱</span><div class="feat-title">Click to navigate</div><p class="feat-desc">Click any static route to jump to it instantly — no URL typing required.</p></div>
          <div class="feat"><span class="feat-icon">🔵</span><div class="feat-title">Active highlight</div><p class="feat-desc">The currently open page is highlighted so you always know where you are.</p></div>
          <div class="feat"><span class="feat-icon">🏷</span><div class="feat-title">Route tags</div><p class="feat-desc">Dynamic params, SSR, endpoints, and redirects all clearly labelled.</p></div>
          <div class="feat"><span class="feat-icon">🔍</span><div class="feat-title">Searchable</div><p class="feat-desc">Filter routes by URL pattern or file path in real time.</p></div>
          <div class="feat"><span class="feat-icon">🔄</span><div class="feat-title">Live updates</div><p class="feat-desc">New pages added while the dev server is running appear on next open.</p></div>
          <div class="feat"><span class="feat-icon">🔒</span><div class="feat-title">Dev-only</div><p class="feat-desc">Completely stripped in <code>astro build</code> — never bundled, never shipped.</p></div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- i18n Toolkit preview -->
      <section class="section">
        <p class="section-eyebrow">astro-i18n-toolkit</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">Translation gaps,<br />caught before they ship.</h2>
        <p class="section-desc">Click the globe icon in the dev toolbar. Every translation key is scanned across all locale files and shown as complete, fallback, or missing — plus a one-click locale switcher.</p>

        <div class="terminal">
          <div class="terminal-bar">
            <span class="t-dot red"></span><span class="t-dot yellow"></span><span class="t-dot green"></span>
