            <div><span class="t-err">  ✗</span>  <span class="t-str">footer.newsletter   </span>  <span class="t-err">missing: es</span></div>
            <div><span class="t-warn">  ~</span>  <span class="t-str">hero.subtitle       </span>  <span class="t-warn">fallback: de</span></div>
            <div><span class="t-ok">  ✓</span>  <span class="t-str">nav.home            </span>  <span class="t-dim">complete</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="features">
          <div class="feat"><span class="feat-icon">🗺</span><div class="feat-title">Coverage map</div><p class="feat-desc">Every key colour-coded: green for complete, amber for fallback, red for missing — per locale.</p></div>
          <div class="feat"><span class="feat-icon">📊</span><div class="feat-title">Per-locale %</div><p class="feat-desc">Coverage percentage badge per locale so you know at a glance which locales need the most work.</p></div>
          <div class="feat"><span class="feat-icon">🌐</span><div class="feat-title">Locale switcher</div><p class="feat-desc">One click switches the active locale via a cookie + middleware redirect. No URL editing required.</p></div>
          <div class="feat"><span class="feat-icon">🔍</span><div class="feat-title">Searchable keys</div><p class="feat-desc">Filter keys by name or reference value in real time across all locales.</p></div>
          <div class="feat"><span class="feat-icon">⚙️</span><div class="feat-title">Library-agnostic</div><p class="feat-desc">Reads JSON or YAML files directly. Works alongside any i18n library — or none at all.</p></div>
          <div class="feat"><span class="feat-icon">🔒</span><div class="feat-title">Dev-only</div><p class="feat-desc">Middleware and toolbar stripped completely in <code>astro build</code>. Zero production footprint.</p></div>
        </div>
      </section>

